comments.body:
@yossigo the real tests that "approve" the release are the ones in the daily CI (include LIBC malloc, 32-bit, valgrind, etc).

also note that in the past, this step was running in some reserved (consistent) bare metal machine, and now i changed it to just run on the local machine.

i intend for this test step to be just an extra sanity (one that actually tests the released tarball). in that respect maybe i should remove the cluster tests which IIRC take a long time.
